## Retrospective Summary
Here's what went well:
  * We each completed our assigned issues 
  * We were able to get an early stage functioning product
  *  
Here's what we'd like to improve:
   * We would like to finish our issues more efficiently
   * We want to improve our communication and teamwork
   * We want to continue to develop our project management skills
 
Here are changes we plan to implement in the next sprint:
   * Work more proactively 
   * Document as we go along and not just at the end
